text: All the residents of BusinessTown are startup versions of Richard Scarry's Busy Town.

attachments.text: Surfancy works by attaching two slim, small-scale, wireless bars to a desired surface that turn it into a live, touch-sensitive area. It comes with user-friendly mobile and PC apps that help you configure the new surface for multiple business and entertainment purposes. Surfancy bars work with any Bluetooth-enabled smartphone or computer and, if needed, can also be connected via a USB cable.
